entries.complete: Another victory earned for Black Epsilon.  Return to base.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_1: Now you will die Imperial aggressor.
entries.duty_update: pcontrast3 Black Epsilon Command: < pcontrast1 %TO pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc: Uploading the coordinates to suspect Rebel activity now.
entries.level_boss: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 A %TO has been spotted, do not let them escape. pcontrast3 >
entries.level_boss_dead: This is a great blow to the Rebellion.
entries.level_increase: More Rebel craft have been detected.
entries.quest_destroy_d: Destroy any Rebel fighters that attack you. Keep a close eye out for the Rebel Captains who will come in to try to take you out if you destroy enough of their men.
entries.quest_location_d: Corellia, although offically neutral, has always been known for harboring members of the Rebellion. Travel to that sector to receive your first Nav location to areas of high Rebel activity.
entries.targets_behind: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 Enemy targets coming fast from behind! pcontrast3 >
entries.targets_detected: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 Enemy targets sighted.  Prepare for assault. pcontrast3 >
entries.taunt_1: The Empire sent you to hunt me? Pathetic!
entries.taunt_2: I hope you have life insurance.
entries.taunt_3: Beg all you want. I will not show mercy.
entries.taunt_4: This is your last chance to flee.
entries.title: Corellia System: Destroy the Rebel Fighters Duty
entries.title_d: Travel to the Corellia system and destroy the Rebel fighters. Black Epsilon believes that it is time to take the fight to the Rebellion. Intelligence has managed to locate several areas of high Rebel activity. You are to travel to these areas and destroy any Rebels that you find in the area.
